Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she was asked the following question in an interview:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That was amazing. What's your secret?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I was just lucky."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that answer would have been very painful for the substitute player to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People should take pride in their own abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, think about how those on the sidelines must feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}extraordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could I have erred in my self-assessment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I really believe in myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Irisu, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to go to school on a holiday. What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something you've gotta do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I go to school without having something I need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just unusual, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received a direct order from Irisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to figure out Kaitou's murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oreki Houtarou is helpful and compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't quite catch that. Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite different from your usual creed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this because of Chitanda again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't do anything I don't have to."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that was your motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel like there's anything that only you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you I have no talents?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, I look up to Sherlockians, but I can't become one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lack that vital spirit needed to delve into the unfathomable maze of knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Mayaka took an interest in Holmes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mark my words,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd outdo me in three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just sample each genre long enough to say I've been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about the most I could do. I couldn't be an expert on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Irisu got you into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see why you'd feel unsure about your own skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never doubt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayaka's probably at the school too, so I'll drop by to say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how you look at yourself, but I think more of you than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put your mind to it, you could become the greatest Sherlockian in Japan one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things more attractive than being a Sherlockian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:40.87,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\fax0.72\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\b0\c&H2F3B3A&\blur0.7\frx18\fry12\frz334.4\org(864,262)\pos(650,304)}Earth {\fax0.7\c&H2B3934&}Sci. Prep. {\fax0.6\c&H272F2D&}room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Jesus Christ on a pogo stick! lol}Oreki voluntarily coming in on a holiday? What is this madness?!{THIS IS SPARTA}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ominous! Like it's foreshadowing some natural disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like solving some mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because a certain person called Irisu coaxed you into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sharp, Mayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how did it go yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean with Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made it home somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I called her this morning, she was suffering from a hangover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... quite a rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's take another look at this movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou's arm was really well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really does look like an arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prop guys were the most talented part of the team, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Damn it! Who did this?{overlap with middle of prev line}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't imagine this being some kind of complicated twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's disguised to look simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't intended to look simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's because the movie itself is so boring
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that it makes the mystery seem uninteresting as well.{HOW META}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A number of volunteers from Class 2-F decided to take part in the Kan'ya fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They are currently on their way to the Narakubo area to gather material for their exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{satoshi}Yeah, it took me a while to realize it was a locked room mystery.{starts right between the above two lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We're still not there?{towards end of previous line}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.23,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\blur1.5\fnSanford\b1\c&H2E4339&\pos(618,450)}Yamanishi      Midori
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.23,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\blur1.2\bord0.8\fnSanford\b1\fnSanford\c&HFFFFFF\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(618,450)}Yamanishi      Midori
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{satoshi}In that way, their performance is quite lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We're close. Should only be about five more minutes.{bg}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{houtarou}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{satoshi}The camera work's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's exactly what you said {\i1}last{\i0} time!{bg}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ibara}Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{houtarou}Then how would you do it, Ibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's quite ti—{bg, cut off}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ibara}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's full of du—{cut off}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be better to frame this shot from further away, to show off more of the hall with the actors?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sugimura! Had any luck up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This one's quite clean. We could use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll come back dow—{cut off}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here, if they took this shot from Sugimura's point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be much clearer that he was overseeing the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The viewers don't get that when the shot's taken from ground level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could do this all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get nowhere if we just complain about technical issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. It might still be worth considering, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you, Fukube!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, messing around over here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hello, Yamaguchi! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, violence isn't the answer, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I have my own priorities too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you? You think Omichi was kidding around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you {\i1}trying{\i0} to get kept down a year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi, you should take your supplementary classes more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Hongou's mystery is important too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Houtarou, quickly, figure it out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That secret! That locked room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's wrong with that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Houtarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's depressing when you realize that some things are just beyond our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fukube!{overlap, link 207+209}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this notebook will have to carry on in my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the love of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time I got going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help you right now, not even for Irisu's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got library duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have kept today open if I'd known this was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for springing it on us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Oreki.{hhhhnnnngggghhhh}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and check the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be a problem. The keys should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was Hongou's true intention.
