Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first question is: have you figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then please elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mystery clearly hinges on the locked room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy – I mean, Kaitou – died in a room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where no one could enter or leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The left wing was a locked room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only connection to the outside was the window, and as you can see...
