Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:44.82,fucking floorplan,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.1\blur0.6\frx38\fry4\pos(644,480)}Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:44.82,fucking floorplan,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.1\blur0.6\frx38\fry4\pos(470,649)}Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:44.82,fucking floorplan,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.1\blur0.6\frx38\fry4\pos(124,385)}Hall
