Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:44.82,fucking floorplan,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.1\blur0.6\pos(75,131)\frx48\fry0}Right wing
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.56,0:14:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the culprit had no choice but to use the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the video we have no way of knowing if there was some kind of physical trick to the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the most logical conclusion is that the culprit used the master key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Sugimura was watching the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:05.80,fucking floorplan,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.1\blur0.76\pos(129,379)\frz324.4\frx34\fry0}Office
