Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.84,0:15:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, the culprit wouldn't even be able to use the right-hand corridor.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, in essence, the second "locked room".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:12.55,fucking floorplan,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\fax-0.1\blur0.76\frz324.4\frx34\fry0\pos(86,363)}Office
